    "## 1. Problem Setup\n",
    "ERA5 is coarse-resolution reanalysis data. PRISM is higher-resolution climate data.\n",
    "The objective is to learn a mapping from ERA5 sequence inputs to PRISM target grids.\n"
   ]
  },
