   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Modeling Approach\n",
    "Models used in this pipeline:\n",
    "- persistence baseline\n",
    "- linear baseline\n",
    "- CNN as spatial baseline\n",
    "- ConvLSTM as temporal model\n",
    "\n",
    "The purpose is to test whether temporal context improves downscaling performance.\n"
   ]
  },
